## 做 Mixin 

利用 css function 做 mixin , 或是直接用 function回傳css字串: 

``` js
import { css } from 'styled-components';

const boxShadowMixin = css`
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
`;

const boxShadowMixinFunc = (top, left, blur, color, inset = false) => {
 return `box-shadow: ${inset ? 'inset' : ''} ${top}px ${left}px ${blur}px ${color};`;
}

const StyledComp = styled.div`
  ${boxShadowMixin}
  ${boxShadowMixinFunc(0, 0, 4, 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)')}
`;
```

## 跟現有 CSS 框架做整合

就是用 attr 加入classname: 

``` js
const Button = styled.button.attrs({
  className: "small",
})`
  background: black;
  color: white;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 1em;
  padding: 0.25em 1em;
  border: 2px solid black;
  border-radius: 3px;
`;
```

